{
  "id": "RAW_e497f2",
  "title": "让远程电脑成为你的 AI 助手 - Computer Use Agent 实践",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MzYzMjE0MQ==&mid=2247514951&idx=1&sn=0442a23f0caa780fd9441ac5eb88eb6d",
  "date": "2025-06-21 04:19:00",
  "author": "弹性计算团队",
  "siteName": "字节跳动技术团队",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px 8px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在人机交互的技术演进中，如何突破传统 API 调用的桎梏，实现更自然、高效的计算机任务执行？Computer Use Agent 给出了答案。只需简单指令，它就能帮你完成视频剪辑、PPT制作、自媒体运营等任务，就像雇佣了一位24小时在线的数字员工。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这款基于字节跳动自研 Doubao-1.5-thinking-vision-pro /Doubao-1.5-UI-TARS &nbsp;模型的 AI 产品，依托 AI 云原生 AgentKit 套件，以强化学习融合视觉能力与高级推理，无需特定 API 即可直连图形用户界面（GUI）。从视频剪辑到 PPT 制作，从自媒体运营到复杂桌面操作，它凭借智能感知、自主推理的行动式 AI 架构，将用户指令转化为精准的自动化任务执行，正引领从 “对话式 AI” 到 “行动式 AI” 的技术变革。</span></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 40px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">感知</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：CUA 截取计算机屏幕图像，旨在对数字环境中的内容进行情境化处理。这些视觉输入成为决策的依据。</span></p></li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">推理</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：CUA 借助思维链推理对其观察结果进行评估，并跟踪中间步骤的进展。通过分析过往和当前的屏幕截图，该系统能够动态适应新的挑战和不可预见的变化。</span></p></li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">行动</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：CUA 利用虚拟鼠标和键盘执行键入、点击和滚动等操作</span></p></li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">同时 Computer Use 已经在社区内部开源，仓库详情：https://github.com/volcengine/ai-app-lab/tree/main/demohouse/computer_use</span></p>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"margin: 24px 0px 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <section style=\"width: 100%;height: 10px;margin-bottom: -6px;background-color: rgb(100, 217, 251);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <svg viewbox=\"0 0 1 1\" style=\"float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;\"></svg>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"line-height: 1em;padding: 0px 8px;font-size: 20px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">让 Agent 像人一样操作电脑</span></strong></p>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px 8px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Computer Use Agent 通过三大核心技术实现自动化操作：</span></p>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2179fbc3-20f4-48e5-71a4-d23a97876a00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.44693396226415094\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"848\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100031301\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2179fbc3-20f4-48e5-71a4-d23a97876a00/public\">\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"font-size: 18px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">系统架构</span></strong></p>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n     <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/36c67727-fcc1-4b2b-7d89-46283af72200/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5138889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-imgfileid=\"100031259\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/36c67727-fcc1-4b2b-7d89-46283af72200/public\">\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"font-size: 18px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">从“感知”到“推理” 再到“执行”</span></strong></p>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px 8px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 Computer Use Agent 完成任务的完整链路中，感知层通过实时截图获取环境状态，推理层基于多模态输入生成决策，执行层则通过原子化操作实现动作反馈。这一流程依赖于以下核心组件的协同运作：</span></p>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n     <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7ef9fead-fd9e-4af8-3d62-8ff3ef918500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5910165\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"846\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-imgfileid=\"100031257\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7ef9fead-fd9e-4af8-3d62-8ff3ef918500/public\">\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);padding: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFangSC-light;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n     <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1ae49c88-0ba9-4e62-199c-057f915f5600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.2703703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100031302\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1ae49c88-0ba9-4e62-199c-057f915f5600/public\">\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 0px 24px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">组件调用时序图</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">用户发起任务后，Planner 通过周期性截图获取沙箱状态实现与 WebUI 交互，并结合历史消息调用模型进行推理；模型返回下一步动作及总结，经 MCP Server调用 Tool Server 在沙箱中执行动作，直至模型返回完成标志 [Finished] 终止流程。整个过程通过“感知-推理-执行”循环实现自主任务处理。</span></span></p>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"font-size: 18px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">技术底座的四大核心能力</span></strong></p>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px 8px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 40px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">强大的自研模型：字节跳动自主研发的 Doubao-1.5-thinking-vision-pro 核心模型，通过自然语言处理与计算机视觉技术的深度融合，实现对用户指令的多维度语义解析，精准捕捉业务需求背后的场景意图，为复杂任务执行提供底层智能支撑。</span></p></li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">多种操作系统支持：提供 Windows 与 Linux 双系统支持，Windows具有无可比拟的传统软件生态，Linux更加轻量与灵活，可以满足企业级计算环境的多元化需求。。</span></p></li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">极致拉起速度：依托字节跳动分布式架构的底层技术积累，通过资源池化管理、热迁移变配等核心能力，实现云主机实例的秒级启动响应。动态负载均衡机制可根据业务流量实时调整资源分配，构建从资源申请到服务就绪的极致弹性链路，显著提升用户操作的实时性体验。</span></p></li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">灵活服务组合：采用高内聚低耦合的微服务架构设计，支持火山 computer-use 方案的全栈式部署与组件化调用，对于大型互联网客户，支持按需编排Agent Planner、MCP Server、Sandbox Manager等服务，对于小型客户，提供全栈式的一体化的解决方案。</span></p></li>\n    </ol>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <section style=\"width: 100%;height: 10px;margin-bottom: -6px;background-color: rgb(100, 217, 251);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <svg viewbox=\"0 0 1 1\" style=\"float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;\"></svg>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"line-height: 1em;padding-left: 2px;padding-right: 2px;font-size: 20px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">场景实战演示</span></strong></p>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"font-size: 18px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">场景1：智能订机票</span></strong></p>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 40px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">用户指令：“订北京→法兰克福6月3日航班，乘机人张三”</span></p></li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI操作：自动打开航司官网→输入地点日期→智能选择经济舱→跳过广告弹窗→完成乘机人认证</span></p></li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 系统提示词确保关键步骤零失误</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p>\n    <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n     <iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_4040199764774895634\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_4040199764774895634\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2F5EcwYhllQOgtqw1Yia1w1Q3kURqeQL5fbNTPJr0Xu6o0z30A5whgG4l5xG7eX0WictF9t0Gx1JXwX2efQJ7iat7gw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.637037037037037\" data-w=\"1768\"></iframe>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"font-size: 18px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">场景2：文件信息整理</span></strong></p>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 40px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">用户指令：“把照片按拍摄国家分类”</span></p></li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI操作：识别埃菲尔铁塔→创建“法国”文件夹→移动相关图片 &nbsp;</span></p></li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 支持100+国家地标图片识别</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p>\n    <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n     <iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_4040201221641224199\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_4040201221641224199\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2F5EcwYhllQOgtqw1Yia1w1Q3kURqeQL5fbFlEib6c8te5ujbCbEDo6piaQuIdGuxyl4cBib159V1hVlkibh9VvXZCJyA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.612962962962963\" data-w=\"1742\"></iframe>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"font-size: 18px;font-family: PingFangSC-light;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">场景3：全球发票处理</span></strong></p>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 40px;list-style-po